{"tid":2432463,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"心美勇奪「封面女郎」話題獎 澤口愛華連獲四獎成大贏家","createTime":"2021-03-04T10:55:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T11:10:49.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b3d47e674ed5d8ec4fdd7d339b77698c09e47bf9","tid":2432463,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T10:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/arhl5tqT-zyqSzSVs1r9r8VzCP4=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RH2FP7HZL5AX3MINEZJ6JDJ7N4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Farhl5tqT-zyqSzSVs1r9r8VzCP4%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRH2FP7HZL5AX3MINEZJ6JDJ7N4.jpg&h=b5941e7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本「第7屆封面女郎大賞」今日佈得獎名單，年僅18歲的水着偶像澤口愛華連奪四獎成大贏家，而日劇天王木村拓哉的大女心美就獲得話題賞。<br />\n<br />\n為記念日本每年3月4日的「雜誌之日」，今日發表的「封面女郎大賞」頒獎表揚去年登上最多雜誌封面的女性藝人，所調查的雜誌大約1萬本。木村拓哉和工藤靜香的大女心美於去年5月首次登上《Vogue Japan》雜誌，成為全國熱話，獲主辦單位頒發「話題獎」，而King &amp; Prince成員平野紫耀就連續兩年獲得男子組大獎。年僅18歲的水着偶像澤口愛華力壓眾星，除了勇奪大獎外，還同時包辦「10代組別」、「漫畫雜誌組別」和「寫真雜誌組別」冠軍，共四個獎項。其他獲獎藝人包括「娛樂組別」的乃木坂46成員與田祐希、「時裝組別」的女星井川遙、「20代組別」的乃木坂46成員齋藤飛鳥和「30代組別」的女星泉里香等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uet8q-_NysiV8rZXiY2ZQn120Yg=/802x1065/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZPZGZPVXPBCQLB4BHKB26BIZX4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fuet8q-_NysiV8rZXiY2ZQn120Yg%3D%2F802x1065%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZPZGZPVXPBCQLB4BHKB26BIZX4.jpg&h=a60556a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fL1xPNQ5W0MuwSu9kjje3gffQLg=/802x802/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RKUWWVZL2BEXDNEFNJ4FQJCBIA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfL1xPNQ5W0MuwSu9kjje3gffQLg%3D%2F802x802%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRKUWWVZL2BEXDNEFNJ4FQJCBIA.jpg&h=bf8b7fdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/epvIvGDoIbTpsfW8p19F3eiTs88=/802x802/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YUDQAYQJP5BHFFHLBQROD5DQSY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FepvIvGDoIbTpsfW8p19F3eiTs88%3D%2F802x802%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYUDQAYQJP5BHFFHLBQROD5DQSY.jpg&h=f186e34e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/msMN_WWFrwnQrrFN0uO6Gc8nt4U=/802x802/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JDH2XG5W5ZCSVHZ455UGVFCYUI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmsMN_WWFrwnQrrFN0uO6Gc8nt4U%3D%2F802x802%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJDH2XG5W5ZCSVHZ455UGVFCYUI.jpg&h=8b3e2475&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Qttc4mHMPZIojlD_d-_p4hWZC9w=/802x802/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZL5TLLU46JDRHJGLJWMTIZN7UM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQttc4mHMPZIojlD_d-_p4hWZC9w%3D%2F802x802%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZL5TLLU46JDRHJGLJWMTIZN7UM.jpg&h=9f4e4ba0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SOzS466Z15GmQN8-uDNnGvCCx6k=/802x802/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BAZ4A2KK5VFWDEJD3XQMI7GCNM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=